notes: Chanderpaul passes his highest ODI score with 150
Chanderpaul and Hooper set the highest WI ODI 4th wicket partnership of 226
Also the highest partnership for any wicket for the West Indies
Also the highest partnership against South Africa by any team
McGarrell (6*) and Semple (1) set their highest ODI scores
Pollock sets his best ODI figures of 6/35
Boucher passes his highest ODI score with 51
Williams plays his 1st ODI match for RSA
King sets his best ODI figures of 3/40

milestones.description: Carl Hooper and Chanderpaul's 226-run partnership is WI's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 149 between Rohan Kanhai and Clive Lloyd
Carl Hooper and Chanderpaul's 226-run partnership is WI's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 221 between Viv Richards and Greenidge
